{
  "entries": [
    {
      "offset": "0x79fbb",
      "back_en": "Lord Oshtor began as a simple lowly soldier, and",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'footman unrank'd' rendered as 'soldado raso'; acceptable."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x79fee",
      "back_en": "young as few, he rose to the post of the",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'unthinkably young' loosely as 'jovem como poucos'; sense preserved."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a022",
      "back_en": "Imperial Guard.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a035",
      "back_en": "A more humble man — so loved among his own —",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faithful."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a065",
      "back_en": "you would rarely come to meet.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sense preserved with archaic register."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a085",
      "back_en": "By faith, milady Rulutieh's trembling has reason,",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'at his presence' omitted; trembling cause is lost."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a0ba",
      "back_en": "for even the Mikado praises his name",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a0fc",
      "back_en": "Alas, there are those who brand milord a parvenu,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faithful."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a131",
      "back_en": "but Maroro — Maroro knows much more.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'far better' as 'muito mais'; minor nuance, acceptable."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a17a",
      "back_en": "Truth be told. Great pride has Maroro in his",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faithful."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a1ac",
      "back_en": "young lord!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a1ce",
      "back_en": "Ah — merely that milord and I share in a",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faithful."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a432",
      "back_en": "How fared thy attack on the bandits' den,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a460",
      "back_en": "Master Ukon?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a552",
      "back_en": "Oho, the good tidings have reached thine ears.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faithful."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7a586",
      "back_en": "All glory to Master Haku for his triumph!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'praise' as 'glória'; acceptable."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7aadc",
      "back_en": "I-Is that true?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sense preserved."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7ab2a",
      "back_en": "H-Hurrah! Fate smiles upon Maroro today!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7abc6",
      "back_en": "Though it shames me to admit, my finances",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'accounts' as 'finanças'; acceptable."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7abf8",
      "back_en": "are fasting on gold lately.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Idiomatic rendering of 'starved of gold'; fine."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7ac22",
      "back_en": "But fortune ever turns! I-I may yet obtain",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'lo' dropped; negligible."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7ac52",
      "back_en": "a new inkstone, brushes, letter-paper!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7ade0",
      "back_en": "Hm? There was nothing offensive",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'particularly' dropped; minor."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7ae13",
      "back_en": "about that comment...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7ae29",
      "back_en": "Eh? What ails you? A filled cup is not so expensive,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faithful."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7ae5d",
      "back_en": "with such riches to my name.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7aedc",
      "back_en": "Wh-What is the matter, friends?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7af2d",
      "back_en": "You needn't be so modest! Let us eat,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faithful."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7af61",
      "back_en": "drink, and be merry together!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7afca",
      "back_en": "D-Do you not desire such festivity?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'revels' as 'festividade'; acceptable."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7afec",
      "back_en": "I implore you! Master Haku! Your company in",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'bosom company' loses intimacy nuance; minor."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7b01d",
      "back_en": "our festivity would be most welcome!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7b19f",
      "back_en": "Th-This is true, but...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sense preserved."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7b1b5",
      "back_en": "If Maroro has aught to offer, let each",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faithful."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7b1e9",
      "back_en": "man receive at least a cup of the finest sake.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7b27b",
      "back_en": "Eh? What do you speak of?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7b307",
      "back_en": "Wh-What? Do you speak the truth?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7b33e",
      "back_en": "N-No! Say not this to me. Say it is a lie...",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "Voice inconsistency: 'digais' (vós) then 'Digam' (vocês)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7b3d1",
      "back_en": "A-And so Maroro descends into the torment of",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate; narrator voice fine."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7b539",
      "back_en": "A-Are you sure?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'Truly?' shifted to 'Tem certeza?'; acceptable nuance."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7ba33",
      "back_en": "M-Master Haku! You would go to such lengths for",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faithful."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x7ba65",
      "back_en": "me... Your generosity warms my heart!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'charity' as 'generosidade' and idiom rendered naturally; fine."
    }
  ],
  "reviewed": 42
}